/* ── Glitch Text ────────────────────────────────────────────
   Uses ::before / ::after pseudo-elements for the RGB layers.
   Customize:
     --nuda-glitch-clr-r  : red channel offset color
     --nuda-glitch-clr-c  : cyan channel offset color
     --nuda-glitch-speed  : animation duration
